public enum PermissionType
extends Enum<PermissionType>

Represents groups of operations that is categorized under a permission type.

Enum Constant Detail

LIST

public static final PermissionType LIST
Allows listing objects belonging to an entity. For example, with this permission on a namespace, the user may list all applications under a namespace.

READ

public static final PermissionType READ
Allows reading data belonging to an entity. For example, with this permission on a dataset, the user may read the data of the dataset.
